parameters: $gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaWoCl^.Where is the orange glow? Where is the gate to Hell?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.Where are the others? Where is Brian?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiWoCl^.I… I don’t know what happened… There was an explosion.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaMaAg.Open the gate! We have to go back!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiShCl^.The bomb… It went off… I must have been pushed through the rift…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiSaEx^.I’m sorry… A human could not have survived that blast.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiSaCl^.I am not fit to be the mother of humanity…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiSaEx^.Send me back to Hell, where I belong.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuSaAg.No! This will not bring Father Solomon back…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuSaEx.She defied the will of God… But haven’t we all?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiSaOp^.I have, too… I put lives at risk.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaAnEx.Go back to Hell and save my father.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaEx^.Use the amulets… I am not fit to be here… But I can not bring him back.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArSaEx^.She can’t do it… It needs to be me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArSaEx^.I must be the one to try and save them.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiAnOp.You’re an angel… You can not go to Hell.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McSaEx.The rift is closed… Our pathway is shut.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArAnEx^.You know what… I think Lilith probably should have been the mother of humanity.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArAnDe^.I… I think she got treated very poorly by God.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiShCl.How can an angel make such a claim?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArAnDe^.And… And I think God can be a real poopy-head sometimes.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArBaEx^.The Oracle… I can use it to go to Empyrean… I can talk directly to God if I want to.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiAnOp.Are you crazy? He has no power in Hell… Even He can’t save them.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiAnDe.If that Oracle were bound to me, I could use it to go to Hell and bring them back.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaEx.But that’s not possible… It’s your portal, not mine.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArBaEx^.The portal brings me home… It brings me to the Empyrean.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeWoOp.What’s going on? What is she saying?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McShCl.The Oracle would bring you to Hell.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiShEx.The Oracle is bound to her, but where it takes her depends on her soul.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaEx.As an angel, it takes her to Empyrean. But as a demon…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Alright, but how does that help Brian and Henry?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.How will you get them out, now that the rift is gone?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArBaEx^.I can take them through the Oracle.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaEx.Well… Arianna did take a relic to Erica in Limbo, did she not?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaDe.That means she can transport something other than herself through the Oracle.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.But if Arianna can only go back and forth between Earth and whatever her home is...");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.... Wouldn’t that mean that humans couldn’t transport at all, since Earth is our home?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArBaEx^.That’s why you were able to visit Hell in the first place, while I could not.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaEx.It means the angel can sacrifice herself in order to bring back the treasure hunter and the priest.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HnFrEx.If you need a goat, I have one at the farm.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.Will those words make her a demon?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArSaOp^.It’s no use… I can not sin on my own… I need help.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaDe.1Hero… You know what needs to be done.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.Wait a minute… I can’t fuck Arianna at a time like this.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HnFlEx.What are you talking about? You’re always down to fuck.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.I’m too shaken up… Sex is the last thing on my mind right now.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrEx^.You can do it, baby. We believe in you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeWoCl.1Hero, please save Brian. Tasha just finally got to know her father, and… I’d miss him, too.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.By the way, it was brave of you back there, turning on Andrea.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.But what will you do once this is all over?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeBaDe.I’m not sure what I’m doing now.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeWoDe.With the deal with Andrea off, and the Guild as good as dead with Duncan off the deep end...");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeSaDe.I'm probably headed off to jail again.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeFlEx.But at least I got to see an angel fuck and then turn into a demon.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CaFlDe.Hot damn, woman. That’s one hot outfit.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaWoOp.Now what? How do we save my dad?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaWoCl.Did you see the priest? Did you see my dad?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I’ll do it… I’ll find Henry and Brian, and bring them back.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArWoCl^.Do you know what to look for?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArHaEx^.The pleasure is all mine… I feel like a new woman.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiFlOp.You’ve broken the chains… This is what your God has hidden from you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaEx.1Hero… I can’t come with you through the portal… But I can be sent back to Hell with the amulets.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.No… I can find him. Give me some time.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoDe.I can hardly believe Arianna chose to become a demon.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuAnDe.But when I see how remorseful Lilith is...");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrEx.Maybe being a demon isn’t such a bad thing.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.Hannah showing up when she did was a surprise.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CaAnDeNo1.I can’t believe that girl. Sneaking off like that and getting herself into trouble.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CaAnEx.Yeah, well, she’ll probably get hurt the next time she tries it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CaSaDe.Anyway… I’m sorry about your dad, 1Hero. Kirk is a handful.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.I haven’t had a chance to ask yet: How are you doing?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.I know you’ve been through a lot recently.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErWoCl.Yeah, this really has been such a long and crazy day.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErSaEx.I died, committed blasphemy by masturbating with a relic, went to Hell…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErBaEx.Then I had sex with demons, and then defeated one of them with the relic I masturbated to…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErFlDe.Spanked myself so I could have my body back and be saved from damnation…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErShDe.And then saved the world by letting a priest throw a water bomb at me while I held a statue I couldn’t look at.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChHaOp.I’m so glad Hannah made it back safe!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.Yeah, I didn’t expect her to come in and save the day like that.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.By shoving a dildo up a demon’s ass.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoOp.I hope you can save Father Solomon and the treasure hunter.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrOp.Of course, darling. You're my big boy.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFlEx.It makes me want to jump on that big boy you have in your pants.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.I’ve had so much sex today, I’m not sure I can handle it right now.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFlDe.You’ve always been so bad at lying to me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrEx.But it’s okay, I know you have people to save. Get going, mister.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeSaEx.I’m sorry your father is such a jerk.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.It’s okay, Heather. At least I'll always have you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.So how does it feel, being a demon now?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArAnClNo1.But I also want to have lots of sex all the time.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.It is. But you have to be careful: If you don’t satisfy your urges, then after a while you could blow up.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrDe.Fortunately, I can help you with your demonic desires.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArWoEx.I guess we’ll just have to have sex all the time.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.I’m glad to see you, too, Arianna.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArBaDe.The Empyrean was my home for so long.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArAnDe.Hell just doesn’t feel the same way to me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArBaEx.So I find myself in-between places, for now.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArShOp.Who was that? Don’t they know they’re going to Hell?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArWoEx.Do you think she wants a sneak peak of her ultimate fate?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArWoEx.Why would she be sneaking into Hell?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiWoDe.Everything feels like waking up from a bad dream.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Don’t worry, Kim. The Toma Leolo is no more, and we were able to save Erica. It’s almost over.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiBaDe.I’m glad Erica is safe now. That was hanging over my head after what happened at the studio.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiSaOp.Things weren’t supposed to turn out this way.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiSaDe.I have a lot to think about.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeFrOp>.Brian... I’m glad you made it back.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiShCl>.This is the soul crystal… You… brought him back.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CaWoOp>.I don’t get it… He’s inside of a rock?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrFlEx^.Ta-da! I learned a new magic trick!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrFrEx^.I’m sorry, everyone… I had a tough choice to make… I had to destroy the rift. It was the only way I could save humanity.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaWoCl.I… I don’t understand… Why can’t I touch you?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrSaEx^.I’m here for you, Tasha… But… my physical being is gone.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoAnOp^.What the hell are you people even talking about?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaDe.At this point, I just take it all in stride.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArFrEx.I couldn’t imagine living in a rock… But at least it’s not Hell.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArFrEx.As long as I have the Oracle, I’m happy to call Earth my new home.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiSaDe>.I wanted nothing more than to be a good mother…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiSaEx>.Because of that, I almost led all of my children to a terrible fate.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaEx.It’s hard being a mother. We want what’s best for our children, and do what we can.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChFrOp^.We all do crazy things for love… I understand that now.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrEx^.The Lord forgives… and so do I.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrOp.Perhaps we all should. Lilith, too, is deserving of forgiveness.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiWoEx.A wonderful moment… But shouldn’t we be getting out of here?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoWoEx^.She’s right. We don’t know how stable this mansion is.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "You can now find this character profile in your album.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElHaCl.Now let’s take another look at the prize…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArBaEx.Something like this should not have been removed from its realm.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElAnDe.I don’t suppose there’s any way I could convince you to give it back?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElBaEx.You know… I think you’re probably right. It’s too dangerous to take stuff from Hell.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArFrOp^.Oh, good! I thought I was going to make you angry.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElFrEx.No issues here. We’re all friends, are we not?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElFlOp.By the way, I could use a friend’s opinion: what do you think of my hairdo?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElFlEx.You should come feel it. It’s silky smooth.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElFlOp.You know, Arianna, you have pretty eyes.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArFrOp^.You are so kind! Such a beautiful and kind woman.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElHaOp.That was fun, but I really should get going. Places to be, you understand.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArWoOp^.It was so nice to gain a new friend!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArFrOp.How lovely. Too bad she couldn’t stay longer.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.What the hell is she up to?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArWoOp.You know, 1Hero… Now that I’m a demon, I’m not sure what to do with myself.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArWoDe.The Empyrean was always my home. I don’t really feel at home in Hell.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.Must be hard, after having lived there for so long.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Maybe a change of environment could help. My place is mighty lonely with just me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArWoDe.I don’t know… Don’t we have to get married first?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArWoCl.Oh, boy… They never covered this in angel class.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArWoDe.Are you sure it won’t be an inconvenience?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlDe.Not at all. It’ll be much easier to fuck you if you’re always around.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArFrOp.Of course… But first, let me head to Hell to return the…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlDeNo4.Ha. Seems like she got one over on us.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlDe.You’ve got a lot to learn, Arianna.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Knowing Ella, she’ll find us, but we’re not finding her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArAnDe.When I see her again, I’m giving her a good spanking.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Come on, Arianna. Let’s go back to my place.");
<center>You can now use the Oracle to travel to Hell.
